      "texte": "<p>On donne $\\cos^2\\alpha + \\sin^2\\alpha = 1$.</p><p>1) Sachant que $\\sin\\alpha = \\frac{3}{5}$, calculer $\\cos\\alpha$.</p><p>2) Sachant que $\\cos\\alpha = \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}$, calculer $\\sin\\alpha$.</p>",
