          },
          {
            "numero": "1.b",
            "texte": "Calculer $\\cos^2\\alpha$ puis $\\cos\\alpha$.",
            "niveau": "easy",
            "reponse": "$\\cos^2\\alpha = 1 - (\\frac{3}{5})^2 = 1 - \\frac{9}{25} = \\frac{16}{25}$. Donc $\\cos\\alpha = \\frac{4}{5}$ (angle aigu)."
